  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/245103.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>在Chrome 28登录桌面版和Android平台之后今天Google正式宣布该版本正式登录iOS平台，本次更新最大的改变就是加强了Chrome和其他iOS平台 上Google应用之间的融合互动</strong>，在Chrome中能够让网页链接跳转到比如Google+，Youtube，Google Maps等其他Google应用中进行处理。此外当你在Chrome中登录之后在其他谷歌应用上就无需第二次登录。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eceab4d/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245103.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A8%E5%8D%8F%E4%BD%9C+Chrome+28%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95iOS%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245103.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A8%E5%8D%8F%E4%BD%9C+Chrome+28%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95iOS%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245103.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A8%E5%8D%8F%E4%BD%9C+Chrome+28%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95iOS%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245103.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A8%E5%8D%8F%E4%BD%9C+Chrome+28%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95iOS%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnb