  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/245102.htm", 
  "description": "<p>《半条命》(Half-Life)的粉丝们欢呼吧！因为酝酿了15年的事情终于到来了！<strong>负责过时(但仍在更新的)MOD协作版《半条命》游戏的Sven Co-op团队，已经被官方(Valve)授予了该游戏完全的访问权限，以便打造一个完全独立的MOD游戏。</strong>此外，修改者还能访问访问《半条命》的原始引擎和扩展。如果觉得合适，他们也能够修改引擎(Opposing Force和Blue Shift)。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eceab4c/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245102.htm&amp;t=Valve%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E3%80%8A%E5%8D%8A%E6%9D%A1%E5%91%BD%E3%80%8B%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%80%85%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E+MOD%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245102.htm&amp;t=Valve%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E3%80%8A%E5%8D%8A%E6%9D%A1%E5%91%BD%E3%80%8B%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%80%85%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E+MOD%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245102.htm&amp;t=Valve%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E3%80%8A%E5%8D%8A%E6%9D%A1%E5%91%BD%E3%80%8B%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%80%85%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E+MOD%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245102.htm&amp;t=Valve%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E3%80%8A%E5%8D%8A%E6%9D%A1%E5%91%BD%E3%80%8B%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%80%85%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E+MOD%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" 